OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,7,FHogg is due to be sentenced after he
OL,8,Fadmitted abusing his estranged wife
OL,9,Fover the course of five years.
OL,11,FHe previously pleaded guilty to a
OL,12,Fsingle charge of domestic abuse of his
OL,13,Fex-partner, Gillian Hogg, when he
OL,14,Fappeared at Selkirk Sheriff Court on
OL,15,FNovember 4.
OL,17,FHe admitted shouting and swearing,
OL,18,Ftracking her movements and sending her
OL,19,Fmessages which were alarming and
OL,20,Fdistressing in nature.
