OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FThe court previously heard he berated
OL,7,FMrs Hogg for "not being fun" after
OL,8,Fgoing on drinking binges with his
OL,9,Fcolleagues, and once sent more than
OL,10,F200 text messages to her in the space
OL,11,Fof a few hours.
OL,13,FHogg will appear at Jedburgh Sheriff
OL,14,FCourt for sentencing on Thursday.
OL,16,FThe 32-year-old had been due to stand
OL,17,Ftrial at Selkirk Sheriff Court on
OL,18,FNovember 4 but pleaded guilty that day
OL,19,Fto a charge of domestic abuse between
OL,20,F2019 and 2024 at locations including
OL,21,FHawick in the Scottish Borders.
