OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FHogg, who plays for French club
OL,7,FMontpellier, now lives abroad and is
OL,8,Fin the process of a divorce, the court
OL,9,Fheard that day.
OL,11,FProsecutor Drew Long said the couple
OL,12,Fmoved to Exeter in 2019 with their
OL,13,Fthree young children, all under three,
OL,14,Fbut Hogg's "behaviour deteriorated" as
OL,15,Fhe went out partying.
