OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FMr Long said Hogg would "shout and
OL,7,Fswear and accuse Mrs Hogg of not being
OL,8,Ffun" for not joining in drinking, and
OL,9,Fthat her family "noticed a change in
OL,10,Fher".In 2022, Mrs Hogg went on a night
OL,11,Fout and was bombarded with text
OL,12,Fmessages from her husband which
OL,13,F"caught the attention of the people
OL,14,Fshe was with", the court heard.
OL,16,FThe following year, the couple moved
OL,17,Fto Hawick in the Borders, but Hogg
OL,18,Fused an app to track his wife and
OL,19,F"questioned her whereabouts" while she
OL,20,Fwas dropping the children off, Mr Long
OL,21,Ftold the court.
