OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FIn 2023, Mrs Hogg decided to leave the
OL,7,Frugby player and sought advice from a
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse service.
OL,10,FThe court heard that in September
OL,11,F2023, Hogg sent so many messages that
OL,12,Fit led Mrs Hogg to have a panic
OL,13,Fattack, and Hogg "sent in excess of
OL,14,F200 texts in a few hours despite being
OL,15,Fasked to leave her alone".
