OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg to be sentenced for domestic abuse
OL,6,FOn February 21 this year, police were
OL,7,Fcalled due to Hogg "shouting and
OL,8,Fswearing" and he was taken into
OL,9,Fcustody and then placed on a bail
OL,10,Forder stipulating not to contact Mrs
OL,11,FHogg, or to enter the family home.
OL,13,FHogg retired from professional rugby
OL,14,Flast July but this summer it was
OL,15,Fannounced he was returning after
OL,16,Fsigning for Montpellier on a two-year
OL,17,Fcontract.
